\n\n회사 측은 미래 성장동력 확보를 위한 투자 확대가 우선이라는 입장이지만, 일부 주주들 사이에서는 \"성과는 커졌는데 일반 주주가 체감할 수 있는 환원은 부족하다\"라는 반발도 확산하는 분위기입니다.\n\n특히 일부 두산에너빌리티 주주들은 회사가 이미 일정 수준의 ...","url":"https://www.imaeil.com/page/view/2026050810573784883","published_at":"2026-05-08T11:04:00","sentiment":"neutral","is_new":true}],"disclosures":[{"date":"2026-05-06T17:17:18","title":"단일판매ㆍ공급계약체결              ","url":"https://dart.fss.or.kr/dsaf001/main.do?rcpNo=20260506800911","is_new":false}],"reports":[],"consensus":{"Q":{"period":"2026년 2분기","latest":266066666666.66998,"is_new":false,"series":[{"date":"2026-04-08","value":283970000000.0},{"date":"2026-04-14","value":279320000000.0},{"date":"2026-04-15","value":276200000000.0},{"date":"2026-04-24","value":275563636363.64},{"date":"2026-04-30","value":265591666666.66998},{"date":"2026-05-04","value":266066666666.66998}]},"Y":{"period":"2026년","latest":1122773333333.3298,"is_new":false,"series":[{"date":"2026-04-08","value":1110321428571.43},{"date":"2026-04-14","value":1095557142857.14},{"date":"2026-04-15","value":1093453333333.33},{"date":"2026-04-24","value":1091653333333.33},{"date":"2026-04-30","value":1123460000000.0},{"date":"2026-05-04","value":1122773333333.3298}]}},"stk_flow":[{"date":"2026-05-08","외인":-254530886000,"개인":308665769000,"기관":-54077423000},{"date":"2026-05-07","외인":135603476000,"개인":-175772382000,"기관":39673434000},{"date":"2026-05-06","외인":32483087000,"개인":50378210000,"기관":-88371309000},{"date":"2026-05-04","외인":-22118945000,"개인":72990340000,"기관":-51398745000},{"date":"2026-04-30","외인":-7937482000,"개인":9493582000,"기관":94307000},{"date":"2026-04-29","외인":30238768000,"개인":-77832680000,"기관":47546045000},{"date":"2026-04-28","외인":21295658000,"개인":3617349000,"기관":-24947131000}]},{"code":"086670","name":"비엠티","market":"KSQ","price":17850.0,"change_pct":3.42,"market_cap":177177047250.0,"fwd_pe":null,"fwd_pb":null,"has_chart":true,"has_new":false,"news":[],"disclosures":[{"date":"2026-05-04T14:57:17","title":"기업설명회(IR)개최              ","url